**Risk Description:** Existing patents may block commercial implementation

**Critical Technology Areas:**
* **Knowledge Graph Technologies:**
  * Neo4j patents on graph database optimization
  * Amazon Neptune patents on cloud graph services
  * Google Knowledge Vault patents on automated knowledge extraction

* **Multi-Agent AI Systems:**
  * IBM patents on agent coordination protocols
  * Microsoft patents on distributed AI architectures
  * Academic patents on multi-agent communication

* **Software Testing Automation:**
  * Selenium patents on browser automation
  * Applitools patents on visual testing
  * Sauce Labs patents on cloud testing infrastructure

**Mitigation Approach:**
* **Professional FTO Analysis** ($15K-25K investment)
* **License Negotiation Strategy** for blocking patents
* **Design-Around Development** for high-risk areas
* **Patent Pool Participation** where applicable

